  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3, W-EP-04 trigger)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is 3. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are assessed; the Equivalency of input parameters factor is recorded as not-assessed on the basis that the assessment team judged it inapplicable to this COU because boundary conditions were derived directly from in-vitro measurements. That judgment is expressed only in narrative text; the factor's encoding retains factorStatus 'not-assessed' rather than the correct 'not-applicable', leaving a material epistemic gap at MRL 3.",
  "modelRiskLevel": 3,
  "assuranceLevel": "Low",
  "couName": "VAD use",
